<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="50600000t" end="58600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">开门</p>
<p begin="58800000t" end="74900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">让我出去</p>
<p begin="75200000t" end="92600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">快开门啊</p>
<p begin="115900000t" end="128800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">已经太迟了</p>
<p begin="144100000t" end="161400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">怎么可能太迟了</p>
<p begin="161600000t" end="178800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">现在…马上去雷姆那里的话</p>
<p begin="179000000t" end="205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">你回去那个房间的理由…</p>
<p begin="205200000t" end="226600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">就在刚刚, 已经完全消失了</p>
<p begin="357400000t" end="384500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="410900000t" end="445300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">你为什么要帮我</p>
<p begin="453600000t" end="486100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">只是看不下去你那凄惨的样子而已</p>
<p begin="489500000t" end="506100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">为什么只有我</p>
<p begin="510300000t" end="532400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">如果是真心想要帮我的话</p>
<p begin="532600000t" end="548300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">为什么不救大家…</p>
<p begin="548600000t" end="560700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">如果是你的话</p>
<p begin="561000000t" end="573100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">应该可以拯救大家的</p>
<p begin="576900000t" end="605500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">为…为什么贝蒂非得做这种事情不可</p>
<p begin="613600000t" end="656200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">贝蒂应该没有<br />一定要帮助谁的理由吧</p>
<p begin="656400000t" end="670300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">这样的话…</p>
<p begin="674300000t" end="701300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">你应该也没有帮助我的理由啊</p>
<p begin="705600000t" end="736900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">谁拜托你救我了</p>
<p begin="757800000t" end="783400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">你知道自己做了什么吗</p>
<p begin="788000000t" end="797100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">有可能因为你的错</p>
<p begin="797400000t" end="820000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">一切努力都白费了</p>
<p begin="820200000t" end="840000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">不管什么都已经无法改变</p>
<p begin="840300000t" end="867000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">变成了这个垃圾一般的现实</p>
<p begin="875800000t" end="909800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">你应该把我杀了才对</p>
<p begin="951200000t" end="964300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">…我不知道</p>
<p begin="974800000t" end="988000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">我真的不知道</p>
<p begin="997200000t" end="1008300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">这样的话, 算了</p>
<p begin="1012400000t" end="1034400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">如果你不愿意帮忙的话</p>
<p begin="1063400000t" end="1074200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">不行</p>
<p begin="1100700000t" end="1117400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">你…为什么</p>
<p begin="1117700000t" end="1133100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">不可能让你这样做的吧</p>
<p begin="1133300000t" end="1154600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">怎么能让你死在这里…</p>
<p begin="1154800000t" end="1173300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">快放开我</p>
<p begin="1296900000t" end="1309700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">为什么…</p>
<p begin="1315900000t" end="1328300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">会在这里…</p>
<p begin="1445900000t" end="1455600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">为什么</p>
<p begin="1465400000t" end="1505000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">为什么你会那么珍惜那本书</p>
<p begin="1519900000t" end="1528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">那该不会…</p>
<p begin="1528700000t" end="1567300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">是魔女教的家伙们拿的书吧</p>
<p begin="1578500000t" end="1596700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">只是很像而已吧</p>
<p begin="1611500000t" end="1645900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">为什么…不否认啊</p>
<p begin="1658600000t" end="1677000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">贝蒂并没有被指示</p>
<p begin="1677200000t" end="1699500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">必须回答那个问题才行</p>
<p begin="1710700000t" end="1732900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">那本书上写了些什么</p>
<p begin="1736900000t" end="1749300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">你到底打算做什么</p>
<p begin="1749600000t" end="1774100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">书上也没有提到那个问题</p>
<p begin="1777600000t" end="1787200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">没有书的话</p>
<p begin="1787500000t" end="1800300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">你就什么都做不了吗</p>
<p begin="1804400000t" end="1831900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">那之前为什么要保护我</p>
<p begin="1832100000t" end="1842200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">那个问题</p>
<p begin="1842500000t" end="1852100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">书上也没有</p>
<p begin="1852400000t" end="1876100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">那我们怎么会像现在这样对话呢</p>
<p begin="1876300000t" end="1898800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">拯救了差点死亡的我又是为什么…</p>
<p begin="1899000000t" end="1907700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我不知道</p>
<p begin="1907900000t" end="1917500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">全部都是…</p>
<p begin="1917800000t" end="1937100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">只要不如那本书上所写</p>
<p begin="1937400000t" end="1949900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">你就不能做吗</p>
<p begin="1956900000t" end="1969300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">…就是这样吧</p>
<p begin="1975600000t" end="1987400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">不, 就是这样</p>
<p begin="1991200000t" end="2004700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">所有的一切</p>
<p begin="2004900000t" end="2026200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">都是遵从了福音书的引导而已</p>
<p begin="2032400000t" end="2057300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">那就是贝蒂一切的生存意义</p>
<p begin="2057500000t" end="2082000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">也是贝蒂存在于此的理由</p>
<p begin="2092600000t" end="2117700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">就连救我</p>
<p begin="2117900000t" end="2142900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">都是书上所指示的吗</p>
<p begin="2143200000t" end="2163900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">包括拯救被诅咒的我</p>
<p begin="2164200000t" end="2180900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">在我一个人无法独自面对时</p>
<p begin="2181100000t" end="2194300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">伸出援手帮助也是吗</p>
<p begin="2194500000t" end="2213800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">开玩笑, 生气吵架</p>
<p begin="2214000000t" end="2230000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">说着蠢话互相打闹的时候也是吗</p>
<p begin="2230300000t" end="2240000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">所以</p>
<p begin="2244700000t" end="2263100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我不就是这样说的吗</p>
<p begin="2266800000t" end="2286100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">至今为止贝蒂所做的一切</p>
<p begin="2286400000t" end="2293900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">所见的一切</p>
<p begin="2294100000t" end="2303600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">所说的一切</p>
<p begin="2303900000t" end="2330800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">通通都是记载在这本书上的内容</p>
<p begin="2331100000t" end="2342800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">像你这样的人</p>
<p begin="2343000000t" end="2370300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">根本不可能动摇贝蒂的内心</p>
<p begin="2370500000t" end="2385700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">别太瞧得起自己了</p>
<p begin="2385900000t" end="2393300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">人类</p>
<p begin="2393600000t" end="2407400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">贝蒂的一切</p>
<p begin="2407600000t" end="2420500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">都是为了母亲</p>
<p begin="2424800000t" end="2434000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">像你这样的</p>
<p begin="2436000000t" end="2444900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">像你这样的</p>
<p begin="2449300000t" end="2455700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">人类</p>
<p begin="2457700000t" end="2463600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">人类</p>
<p begin="2465100000t" end="2474400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">人类</p>
<p begin="2565100000t" end="2581300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">不要碰贝蒂, 人类</p>
<p begin="2586000000t" end="2605400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">我不管你了, 人类</p>
<p begin="2608800000t" end="2621800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">讨厌你, 讨厌你</p>
<p begin="2626200000t" end="2641400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">最讨厌你了</p>
<p begin="2712300000t" end="2722500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">那个时候</p>
<p begin="2732200000t" end="2749400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">我是真的很开心</p>
<p begin="2787500000t" end="2799600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">真可惜啊</p>
<p begin="2903200000t" end="2919500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">碧…翠</p>
<p begin="2933900000t" end="2945000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">真棒</p>
<p begin="2948900000t" end="2965700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">看来他很重视你呢</p>
<p begin="3221300000t" end="3232300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">爱蜜莉…雅</p>
<p begin="3292600000t" end="3321100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">重生的时间点并没有改变</p>
<p begin="3328000000t" end="3342800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">这是第三次了吗…</p>
<p begin="3362700000t" end="3372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3372400000t" end="3387600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">不, 不是这样的</p>
<p begin="3387800000t" end="3398500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">-不是我<br />-爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3398800000t" end="3405900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">振作一点</p>
<p begin="3406200000t" end="3416200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">-帕克救我<br />-爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3421300000t" end="3430800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">-帕克<br />-爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3481000000t" end="3491300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">昴</p>
<p begin="3674100000t" end="3692500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">对不起, 昴</p>
<p begin="3696100000t" end="3704200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">我…</p>
<p begin="3704400000t" end="3718900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">刚刚混乱成那样</p>
<p begin="3719200000t" end="3728800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">没什么</p>
<p begin="3729000000t" end="3740800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">没事的啦</p>
<p begin="3743900000t" end="3760200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">但是, 我…</p>
<p begin="3766000000t" end="3783500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">今天就好好休息</p>
<p begin="3783700000t" end="3798800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">明天再说吧</p>
<p begin="3819400000t" end="3827400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">嗯</p>
<p begin="3852400000t" end="3861600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">拉姆</p>
<p begin="3865100000t" end="3878600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">爱蜜莉雅就拜托你了</p>
<p begin="3945800000t" end="3969200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">接着就去和罗兹瓦尔谈话吧</p>
<p begin="3969500000t" end="3993400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">这次绝对要和他问一问上次没问到的</p>
<p begin="3993700000t" end="4017000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">-碧翠丝的事情才行<br />-菜月先生, 菜月先生</p>
<p begin="4017300000t" end="4026100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">你有在听吗</p>
<p begin="4035300000t" end="4043500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">菜月先生</p>
<p begin="4043700000t" end="4055600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你没事吗</p>
<p begin="4069300000t" end="4081100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">那当然啦</p>
<p begin="4081400000t" end="4104600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">很好很好状态超棒的</p>
<p begin="4109400000t" end="4127500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">还是我有哪里看上去很奇怪的吗</p>
<p begin="4134700000t" end="4160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不, 是没有</p>
<p begin="4160300000t" end="4179100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">看上去满冷静的</p>
<p begin="4182200000t" end="4192300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">是吧</p>
<p begin="4192600000t" end="4199000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">那样的话…</p>
<p begin="4199300000t" end="4226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">不过爱蜜莉雅大人<br />现在是那个样子呢</p>
<p begin="4235200000t" end="4264200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">你这样不是反而很危险吗</p>
<p begin="4282900000t" end="4293900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">你的意思是说</p>
<p begin="4294100000t" end="4321400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">我有点太过冷静了吗</p>
<p begin="4321700000t" end="4334900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">是的</p>
<p begin="4335100000t" end="4355800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">虽然我觉得应该不是坏事</p>
<p begin="4356000000t" end="4364700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">可是…</p>
<p begin="4386500000t" end="4403600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不, 因为你这番话</p>
<p begin="4403900000t" end="4418300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">让我找回自信了</p>
<p begin="4418500000t" end="4434900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">谢谢你啦, 奥托</p>
<p begin="4445200000t" end="4460900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">那就是经过了那么多事以后</p>
<p begin="4461200000t" end="4492100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">我终于可以冷静下来<br />思考的最佳证据</p>
<p begin="4495200000t" end="4505000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">不, 那个…</p>
<p begin="4505300000t" end="4543500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">我觉得看上去冷静跟可以冷静的行动之间</p>
<p begin="4543700000t" end="4582000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">可是有一道很深的鸿沟啊…</p>
<p begin="4582300000t" end="4602500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">对手可是那个罗兹瓦尔啊</p>
<p begin="4605800000t" end="4630000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">这次可没有拐弯抹角的余地</p>
<p begin="4635700000t" end="4651600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">能稍微聊一聊吗</p>
<p begin="4656900000t" end="4669900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">加菲尔吗</p>
<p begin="4677000000t" end="4687200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">你还真的是常常</p>
<p begin="4687500000t" end="4706400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">不按牌理出牌呢</p>
<p begin="4714400000t" end="4732800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">在说之前我如果没叫住你的话</p>
<p begin="4733000000t" end="4753900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你都会叫我赶快回去的事啦</p>
