<p begin="6276800000t" end="6282300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">这样的话</p>
<p begin="6282600000t" end="6304000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">即使不接受"试炼"也ok对吧</p>
<p begin="6307100000t" end="6330000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">理论上是如此没错</p>
<p begin="6330300000t" end="6360400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">不过干嘛这么固执的要避开"试炼"呢</p>
<p begin="6360700000t" end="6383700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">我不想让爱蜜莉雅继续接受"试炼"</p>
