<p begin="8897600000t" end="8919400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">应该没有求救的必要吧</p>
<p begin="8930500000t" end="8950000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">我听不懂你在说什么…</p>
<p begin="8950300000t" end="8966700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">你们这些家伙真的是一模一样</p>
<p begin="8967000000t" end="8993000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">都是因为脑袋怪怪的才有名的吧</p>
<p begin="8993200000t" end="9001800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">等等…</p>
<p begin="9002000000t" end="9010400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">到底…</p>
<p begin="9010700000t" end="9018500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">在说什么…</p>
<p begin="9018700000t" end="9029800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">别装傻了</p>
<p begin="9030100000t" end="9062300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">体内散发出那么多瘴气</p>
<p begin="9062500000t" end="9077600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">你这魔女教徒</p>
<p begin="9087400000t" end="9102700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">从墓所出来的时候</p>
<p begin="9102900000t" end="9123000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">那臭味就变得更加浓烈了</p>
<p begin="9129000000t" end="9157200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">我也不是多讨厌瘴气浓烈的家伙</p>
<p begin="9161700000t" end="9179500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">所以如果你什么都不做的话</p>
<p begin="9179700000t" end="9192000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">就这样放过你也可以</p>
<p begin="9194800000t" end="9221400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">但是竟然说要代替公主大人<br />去接受"试炼"</p>
<p begin="9226700000t" end="9237700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="9249900000t" end="9262300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">我身体里</p>
<p begin="9269700000t" end="9288500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">散发的魔女的残香</p>
<p begin="9295300000t" end="9316700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">这称呼还满有趣的嘛</p>
<p begin="9321400000t" end="9334300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">很合适啊</p>
<p begin="9334600000t" end="9352100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">魔女的残香</p>
<p begin="9356300000t" end="9378900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">你进墓所打算做什么</p>
<p begin="9385100000t" end="9399600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">在盘算什么</p>
<p begin="9399800000t" end="9414400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">那可是魔女的坟墓啊</p>
<p begin="9414600000t" end="9432700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">肯定不是在想些什么好事吧</p>
<p begin="9433000000t" end="9464300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">那样的话为什么要把我关起来</p>
<p begin="9467400000t" end="9485000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">为什么不杀了我</p>
<p begin="9493000000t" end="9529900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">毕竟你这家伙和身边的人<br />相处的还不错</p>
<p begin="9535100000t" end="9570700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">我可不想变成像"特斯拉城寨沦陷"那样</p>
<p begin="9570900000t" end="9591000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">因为傻傻的出手而引起众怒啊</p>
<p begin="9591200000t" end="9611800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">那你打算做什么</p>
<p begin="9612000000t" end="9621300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">我只能说</p>
<p begin="9621500000t" end="9649500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">总之就先看看爱蜜莉雅大人的状况</p>
<p begin="9739500000t" end="9754200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">才不会让你得逞</p>
<p begin="9754500000t" end="9770600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">我可不准你自杀</p>
<p begin="9770900000t" end="9807900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">你说不定在盘算些什么呢</p>
<p begin="9813300000t" end="9855400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">本大爷最不爽的就是你那个态度</p>
<p begin="9855600000t" end="9868600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">那个眼神</p>
<p begin="9868900000t" end="9894200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">简直和罗兹瓦尔那家伙一模一样</p>
<p begin="9894400000t" end="9924400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">可别想做些奇怪的事哦</p>
<p begin="9983300000t" end="10000900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">昴大人</p>
<p begin="10004300000t" end="10017300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">昴大人</p>
<p begin="10033300000t" end="10050700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">昴</p>
<p begin="10120300000t" end="10134100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">拉姆, 如何</p>
<p begin="10140800000t" end="10152900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">非常抱歉…</p>
<p begin="10156400000t" end="10179700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">一个人进入了夜晚的迷路森林</p>
<p begin="10179900000t" end="10205300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">可不是那么简单就能出来的啊</p>
<p begin="10208800000t" end="10219300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">一个人</p>
<p begin="10239100000t" end="10253690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">不, 没什么</p>
<p begin="10257400000t" end="10291500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">帕克, 为什么不出来呢</p>
<p begin="10299300000t" end="10320000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">小哥, 稍微过来一下</p>
<p begin="10352000000t" end="10375690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">别说些多余的事</p>
<p begin="10375890000t" end="10389900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">那样的话…</p>
<p begin="10488300000t" end="10517600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">这锁得还真是紧得要死啊</p>
<p begin="10582800000t" end="10615100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">现在可不是被关在这的时候啊</p>
<p begin="10619300000t" end="10630000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">…仔细想想吧</p>
<p begin="10630300000t" end="10644400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">目前知道的是</p>
<p begin="10644600000t" end="10683300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">袭击是等有人回到宅邸后才进行的</p>
<p begin="10683600000t" end="10706200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">从现在这个时间点开始最长5天</p>
<p begin="10757700000t" end="10797700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">你真的只是服从福音书而已吗</p>
<p begin="10801900000t" end="10809900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">所以</p>
<p begin="10810100000t" end="10827700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我不就是这样说的吗</p>
<p begin="10840700000t" end="10859200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">就算真的是这样</p>
<p begin="10868100000t" end="10905100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">我还是好想听听你的声音啊</p>
<p begin="11673200000t" end="11700100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">虽然想过状况可能会满惨的</p>
<p begin="11700300000t" end="11727600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">但看来比我想的还要严重啊</p>
<p begin="11749200000t" end="11763300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">可别发出声音哦</p>
<p begin="11770900000t" end="11795400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">因为我也是冒着生命危险跑来的</p>
<p begin="11795600000t" end="11817800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">我可不想在这里被守卫给抓住啊</p>
<p begin="11822900000t" end="11831300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">毕竟我们</p>
<p begin="11834500000t" end="11853300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">都是不太擅长放弃的人对吧</p>
<p begin="11886500000t" end="11899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">不论如何</p>
<p begin="11900100000t" end="11921700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">看到你还活着真是让我松了一口气</p>
<p begin="11922000000t" end="11932800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">菜月先生</p>
<p begin="11984400000t" end="11999200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">现在已经过几天了</p>
<p begin="11999400000t" end="12012900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">从那之后3天了</p>
<p begin="12016400000t" end="12026100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">现在外面是晚上</p>
<p begin="12030600000t" end="12043600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">是进行"试炼"的时间</p>
<p begin="12043900000t" end="12055700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">3天</p>
<p begin="12056000000t" end="12083800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">而且"试炼"也还在继续吗</p>
<p begin="12087000000t" end="12096500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="12096800000t" end="12114600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">好像有什么想法了哦</p>
<p begin="12120200000t" end="12135300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">我不在的时候</p>
<p begin="12135500000t" end="12149000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">到底发生了什么</p>
<p begin="12149300000t" end="12171500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">菜月先生失踪的消息一下就传开了</p>
<p begin="12171800000t" end="12193200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">村里的大家都很慌张</p>
<p begin="12200100000t" end="12228200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">特别是爱蜜莉雅大人更是慌乱</p>
<p begin="12228400000t" end="12263800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">连隔天"试炼"的挑战都直接放弃了呢</p>
<p begin="12264100000t" end="12276100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">爱蜜莉雅吗</p>
<p begin="12281500000t" end="12303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">大家虽然各自分头去搜索</p>
<p begin="12303200000t" end="12318400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">但是都找不到菜月先生</p>
<p begin="12322900000t" end="12361600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">于是边境伯和爱蜜莉雅大人提出了建议</p>
<p begin="12365200000t" end="12386700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">为了要派出大规模的搜索队</p>
<p begin="12386900000t" end="12412900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">应该以"圣域"的解放为最优先</p>
<p begin="12416400000t" end="12429000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">搜索队…</p>
<p begin="12435800000t" end="12455500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">所以爱蜜莉雅接受那个提案了吗</p>
<p begin="12455700000t" end="12492800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">边境伯那边已经提出了正式的誓约</p>
<p begin="12503500000t" end="12515900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">然后, 昨天和今天</p>
<p begin="12516200000t" end="12551000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">爱蜜莉雅大人都用鬼气逼人的气势去挑战</p>
<p begin="12559100000t" end="12577900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">即使如此还是没能通过试炼</p>
<p begin="12578100000t" end="12601200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">那个痛苦万分的模样<br />看上去非常难受</p>
<p begin="12606800000t" end="12616700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">从刚刚开始</p>
<p begin="12616900000t" end="12635100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">我就稍微有点在意</p>
<p begin="12635300000t" end="12643900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">什么</p>
<p begin="12658900000t" end="12688500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">为什么你的说明<br />好像也是听人家说的一样啊</p>
<p begin="12704500000t" end="12720100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">你是要问这个啊</p>
<p begin="12723700000t" end="12746700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">虽然有点难以启齿</p>
<p begin="12752600000t" end="12765600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">其实我现在</p>
<p begin="12768900000t" end="12791900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">也被加菲尔盯上了</p>
<p begin="12792100000t" end="12819200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">正在到处逃跑当中</p>
<p begin="12822400000t" end="12830500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">什么</p>
<p begin="12834900000t" end="12868100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我不是看到你们两人<br />最后碰面的场景了吗</p>
<p begin="12877000000t" end="12890900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">当然我也怀疑了一下</p>
<p begin="12894600000t" end="12915700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">然后他就对我说了</p>
<p begin="12920300000t" end="12950200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">只要对他有和菜月先生<br />见过面的事情保密</p>
<p begin="12950500000t" end="12973500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">就不会加害于我</p>
<p begin="12980000000t" end="12989200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">做为报酬</p>
<p begin="12989400000t" end="13007700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">他还给我看了一些魔石</p>
<p begin="13008000000t" end="13030800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">但是你却拒绝了吗</p>
<p begin="13036400000t" end="13045400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">好痛…</p>
<p begin="13049900000t" end="13077600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">所以就被加菲尔追杀了吗</p>
<p begin="13081500000t" end="13089100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">是的</p>
<p begin="13089400000t" end="13123600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">所以这些情报全部都是边逃边收集</p>
<p begin="13123900000t" end="13138900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">从别人那里听到的</p>
<p begin="13142400000t" end="13162500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">不过, 虽然很有气势的拒绝</p>
<p begin="13162700000t" end="13176800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">但也因为这样落到这步田地了</p>
<p begin="13177100000t" end="13191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">还请多多包涵啦</p>
<p begin="13191300000t" end="13203200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">别敷衍我</p>
<p begin="13203400000t" end="13213600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">你是笨蛋吧</p>
<p begin="13213900000t" end="13230500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">为什么要做这种事</p>
<p begin="13246600000t" end="13261900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">你愿意来救我</p>
<p begin="13262200000t" end="13277400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">我真的是发自内心感谢你</p>
<p begin="13284900000t" end="13304100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">说真的在看到你的脸之前</p>
<p begin="13304400000t" end="13333400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">我都已经觉得不如死了算了</p>
<p begin="13341000000t" end="13350700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">但是…</p>
<p begin="13359500000t" end="13390600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">我实在找不到你要救我的理由</p>
<p begin="13445100000t" end="13466500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">那个呢, 菜月先生</p>
<p begin="13476900000t" end="13501600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">想帮助友人</p>
<p begin="13507700000t" end="13530000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">是这么奇怪的一件事吗</p>
<p begin="13589100000t" end="13624600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">你这个人为什么要一副惊讶的样子<br />定格在那边啊</p>
<p begin="13629400000t" end="13635800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">不…</p>
<p begin="13639400000t" end="13665000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">因为突然出现了我没听过的人名</p>
<p begin="13665200000t" end="13687800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">这位"有仁"是谁啊</p>
<p begin="13688000000t" end="13717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">你的结论从头到尾都错了啦</p>
<p begin="13717500000t" end="13739800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">不是"有仁", 是"友人"啦</p>
<p begin="13740000000t" end="13754000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">朋友</p>
<p begin="13759000000t" end="13771400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">朋友</p>
<p begin="13776300000t" end="13788500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">谁跟谁</p>
<p begin="13788800000t" end="13794900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">我</p>
<p begin="13795200000t" end="13807600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">和菜月先生啦</p>
<p begin="13847000000t" end="13858200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">确实</p>
<p begin="13858500000t" end="13889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">我们会来到这里是因为利害关系一致</p>
<p begin="13889200000t" end="13901100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">像是油的事情</p>
<p begin="13901300000t" end="13923200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">或是从魔女教手中得救的事情</p>
<p begin="13923400000t" end="13948700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">还是为了和边境伯会面的事情</p>
<p begin="13952100000t" end="13986800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">但是把这些麻烦的事先摆一边的话</p>
<p begin="13987100000t" end="14023200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">我觉得我和菜月先生就只是<br />单纯的友人而已</p>
<p begin="14030700000t" end="14060100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">虽然平常遭受的待遇<br />常会让我有点怀疑</p>
<p begin="14064400000t" end="14093300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">但是这也是友人之间的距离感吧</p>
<p begin="14146000000t" end="14154100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">什么</p>
<p begin="14176700000t" end="14195900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">朋朋朋…朋友</p>
<p begin="14196100000t" end="14209100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">朋友吗</p>
<p begin="14209300000t" end="14225400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">原来如此, 原来如此</p>
<p begin="14225600000t" end="14235300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">奥托</p>
<p begin="14239200000t" end="14271400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">原来你想和我成为朋友啊</p>
<p begin="14292900000t" end="14301400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">朋友</p>
<p begin="14307100000t" end="14318300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">可恶</p>
<p begin="14318500000t" end="14347000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">-奥托, 你这家伙<br />-好痛, 好痛</p>
<p begin="14359400000t" end="14372700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">干嘛啦</p>
<p begin="14378900000t" end="14397300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">说了这些话的我真是大笨蛋</p>
<p begin="14397600000t" end="14411600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">菜月先生一定会笑我这点</p>
<p begin="14411800000t" end="14428900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">我还是知道的</p>
<p begin="14429100000t" end="14456500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">不不不, 这不能不笑吧</p>
<p begin="14456700000t" end="14476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">不是你很奇怪啦</p>
<p begin="14476500000t" end="14501100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">我只是对自己太过白痴这点</p>
<p begin="14501300000t" end="14527400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">给吓到只能笑了而已</p>
<p begin="14614400000t" end="14627400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">菜月先生</p>
<p begin="14663800000t" end="14675600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">抱歉</p>
<p begin="14679100000t" end="14709500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">你是我的朋友哦, 奥托</p>
<p begin="14736300000t" end="14763600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">谢谢你来救我</p>
<p begin="14767800000t" end="14801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">(友人)</p>
<p begin="15525600000t" end="15532400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">现在的话</p>
<p begin="15532700000t" end="15547300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">加菲尔应该在墓所</p>
<p begin="15547500000t" end="15570300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">菜月先生就赶快逃出去结界外面吧</p>
<p begin="15582000000t" end="15607600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">问题是到底做不做得到</p>
<p begin="15607900000t" end="15633500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">不用担心那件事</p>
<p begin="15637600000t" end="15657900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">有个令人心安的协力者在</p>
<p begin="15661500000t" end="15672500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">协力者</p>
<p begin="15724300000t" end="15752300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">等到我觉得都快变成老婆婆了</p>
<p begin="15764900000t" end="15773800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">不过说真的</p>
<p begin="15774100000t" end="15795500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">老了的拉姆应该还是很可爱吧</p>
</div>
